The 35th European Club Cup is a 7-round Swiss tournament taking place from 10-16 November 2019 in Ulcinj, Montenegro.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: sahcg.me/euclubcup
